description: Former Los Angeles Dodgers left-handed pitcher Julio Urias was sentenced to 36 months probation after pleading no contest to misdemeanor domestic battery.

description: The start of jury selection has been delayed in the first civil trial stemming from the Astroworld festival in 2021, where 10 people died in a crowd surge at a concert by rapper Travis Scott.

description: Environmental Conservation Officers on Long Island, New York, have been catching poachers after anglers were reeling in out-of-season striped bass and hiding them.
title: New York officers ticket striped bass poachers after discovering illegal catches hidden in odd places
